        Represents the edge between stages.
        Parameters:
        irEdgeId - id of this edge.
        edgeProperties - to control the data flow on this edge.
        srcStage - source runtime stage.
        dstStage - destination runtime stage.
        coder - coder.
        isSideInput - flag for whether or not the edge is a sideInput.
